NAME

    wxchordpro - a simple Wx-based GUI for ChordPro

DESCRIPTION

wxchordpro is a GUI wrapper for the ChordPro program. It allows
opening of files, make changes, and preview (optionally print) the
formatted result.

For more information about the ChordPro file format, see
http://www.chordpro.org .

For more information about ChordPro program, see
https://metacpan.org/pod/App::Music::ChordPro .

